{"id":413,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":15,"title":"15. Can You Help Me?","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":11,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me.413/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me-2022-03-07-21-09-09/0-15-can-you-help-me.mp3","transcript":"Can you help me, officer?\nI'll try. What's the problem?\nI can't get into my car.\nWhere are your keys?\nThey're in the car.\nDon't worry. I can open it.\nHow can you do that?\nWith a coat hanger. It's easy.\nWhere can we get a coat hanger?\nThere's one in the police car. Wait here.\nThanks a lot! You're very kind.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:30","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Can you help me, officer?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me-2022-03-07-21-09-09/1.mp3","time_start":1.89,"time_end":3.39},{"position":2,"content":"I'll try. What's the problem?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me-2022-03-07-21-09-09/2.mp3","time_start":3.39,"time_end":4.79},{"position":3,"content":"I can't get into my car.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me-2022-03-07-21-09-09/3.mp3","time_start":4.79,"time_end":6.73},{"position":4,"content":"Where are your keys?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me-2022-03-07-21-09-09/4.mp3","time_start":6.73,"time_end":7.86},{"position":5,"content":"They're in the car.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me-2022-03-07-21-09-09/5.mp3","time_start":7.86,"time_end":9.07},{"position":6,"content":"Don't worry. I can open it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/15-can-you-help-me-2022-03-07-21-09-09/6.mp3","time_start":